data.description: Newly Built in May of 2023. Do to life changing circumstances, Sellers are looking to relocate. This home is loaded with benefits, All appliances will stay with the home including the new Samsung washer and dryer. The home is extremely energy efficient. Luxury vinyl plank flooring through out the home with carpet in the bedrooms. Granite counter tops in the kitchen, Double vanity in the master bedroom with a spacious walk in closet. The home also has an irrigation system built in under ground. Not to mention that the H.O.A covers the Grass maintenance. You'll never have to cut your grass again!! Scheduled your showing today and see this beauty that sits on the edge of the cul-da-sac. SELLER IS ALSO OFFERING $5,000 in CLOSING COSTS!!!! OR TO BUY DOWN INTEREST RATE!!!!
